        "text_aap4QN": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every year, millions of tonnes of clothing and textiles are discarded, often long before they have reached the end of their potential. Behind every unwanted garment sits material, energy, craftsmanship and human effort that has simply been written off.</p><p>We found that difficult to ignore.</p><p>Neuthread began with a belief that there was another story waiting to be told. Not by creating more, but by looking differently at what already exists.</p><p>Our garments start with textiles that have already lived a life. Materials that have been overlooked, donated or destined for disposal are carefully recovered and transformed into contemporary pieces designed to be worn, valued and kept.</p><p>This approach shapes everything we do. We work with existing materials, produce in controlled quantities and focus on longevity rather than replacement.</p><p>But Neuthread was never only about materials.</p><p>Developed through Daisy Chain, the brand creates opportunities for autistic and neurodivergent people to contribute to the future of fashion through design, production and creativity. We believe different perspectives strengthen industries, challenge convention and inspire innovation.</p><p>Every Neuthread garment represents something preserved, something reimagined and something made possible.</p><p>We are not trying to make fashion perfect.</p><p>We are trying to prove that it can be made differently.</p><p>And that different can be desirable.Measuring What Matters</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "none",
            "alignment": "left",
            "type_preset": "custom",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
            "font_size": "1rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
