        "text_7rcAtQ": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>he future of sustainable fashion will belong to brands that can prove their impact, not simply talk about it.</p><p>That is why Neuthread is pioneering the development of an innovative impact measurement platform designed to bring unprecedented transparency to every garment we create. Working alongside leading research and technology partners, we are developing a system that will allow customers to understand the environmental story behind their purchase at the touch of a button.</p><p>Rather than broad claims or generic industry estimates, our ambition is to provide garment-level insight into material reuse, resource preservation and environmental impact through a simple, beautifully designed customer experience.</p><p>Still in development, this technology represents the next chapter of Neuthread's journey—where craftsmanship, design and data come together to create a new level of connection between people and the clothes they choose to wear.</p><p>Because the future of fashion is not only about knowing what you are buying.</p><p>It is about understanding the difference it makes.</p><p>And while others are still talking about sustainability, Neuthread is helping define what the next generation of fashion transparency looks like.</p>",
            "width": "100%",
